Description:
EXCLUSIVE YARRAS EDGE
This apartment is perfect for owner-occupiers and CBD professionals who will love its easy care nature and great riverside location. The apartment has a generous lounge and dining opens which opens out to a large balcony, which is a great outdoor space that can be used all year long thanks to its privacy and inspired views of the marina below.
The standout modern style combines with a thoughtful open layout and low-maintenance feel to produce this sensational north-facing two bedroom apartment, which is located in the highly sought-after Yarra's Edge precinct.
It's well-appointed kitchen delivers a sleekly tiled splashback, stone surfaces, island bench, and stainless steel appliances, meanwhile both bedrooms have mirrored built-in robes including the ultra-spacious main bedroom. The 2nd bedroom also has direct balcony access. Other highlights include a bathroom with European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom, secure car space on the same floor for easy access.
You have the short walk to South Wharf attractions including DFO shopping and restaurants and bars including Bangpop, Munich Brauhaus, The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard just to name a few. You're also close to Crown Casino with world class restaurants, CBD, and transport including Southern Cross Station and trams on Spencer Street.
You will also have access to a wonderful roof top facility along with the access to the RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
To inspect please call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

90m²

Exceptional top floor views for eager Docklands dwellers
Located in the exceptional H1 complex and offering stunning 22nd floor views of Marvel Stadium and Victoria Harbour, this tastefully modern 2 bedroom apartment in the heart of the NewQuay precinct is a prize for passionate Docklands lovers!
Outstanding living highlights include an open lounge and dining zone, inviting southerly balcony with spectacular water views that is ideal for outdoor meals, both bedrooms featuring mirrored built-in robe storage, stone-featured kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, well-appointed bathroom, laundry facilities, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, and a secure car space,
H1 facilities include a library lounge, media room, and gym. You also have an amazing location right near The District Docklands, wonderful waterside restaurants for casual dining, Marvel Stadium which is great for footy lovers, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, IGA X-Press supermarket, and trams across Melbourne.

Utter Sophistication with wonderful park views
Located in the exclusive Mosaic complex and offering a spacious living experience right in the heart of the Victoria Harbour precinct, this smart and stylish two bedroom, two bathroom park side residence is the Docklands home youve been searching for.
Apartment sits on a fantastic 108sqm (approx.) allotment
Make the most of incredible east-facing views towards the CBD, Docklands Park and Marvel Stadium
Views are best enjoyed from the sizeable undercover balcony
Expansive lounge and meals will be a delight for everyday living

2nd bedroom also with a BIR plus study nook

2nd balcony with scenic views of the community park below
Separate laundry room
Reverse cycle heating and cooling
Brand new carpet and paint throughout

Secure car space

Description:
Golden Opportunity
With a promise to deliver sophisticated modern character, stunning quality, and a convenient waterside location next to Victoria Harbour, this one spacious bedroom apartment in Aqui Promenade development is a rare opportunity!
Positioned on the 19th level of the Gold Aqui Tower, this brilliant Docklands residence delivers stylishly contemporary interiors and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light. The spacious living and meals zone is well-served by a sleek kitchen with appliances and opens to an undercover balcony for alfresco delights all year round. A spacious bedroom with built-in robes is complemented by a handy study nook and stunning central bathroom. Also included are European laundry, heating/cooling, lift access & intercom.
Ideal to invest or owner-occupy, luxurious residents facilities include a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden and secure on-site bicycle storage. Perfectly positioned moments from trams, cafes and restaurants, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Etihad Stadium, Southern Cross Station and Melbourne's CBD.

Description:
Live the high life! Waterside retreat with spectacular views!
Favourably positioned on the 26th level of the sought after Quays north complex, this 2-bedroom apartment with spectacular city and harbour views will be sure to impress even the most discerning buyer. Perfect for those seeking a convenient, inner city lifestyle, with access to a number of resort style facilities and a stones throw from The District Shopping Centre, Marvel Stadium , New Quay Promenade restaurants and cafes, local trams within the free tram zone, and Southern Cross Station.
This apartment ticks all of the boxes! Not only does it possess space and elegance, but it also draws in excellent natural light via its floor-to-ceiling windows. Featuring a free-flowing open plan living/dining area that leads to a private balcony with enviable views of New Quay, a modern kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances and ample storage space, a contemporary bathroom with mosaic tiles plus two well-sized bedrooms both equipped with built-in robes and an ensuite in the master.
Additional features include, a European laundry, a split system heating/cooling and one secure parking space.
Whether youre a savvy investor or an astute owner occupier, this is an opportunity not to miss!
Facilities:
- 25 meter indoor swimming pool.
- Spa, sauna.
- Fully equipped gym.
- Yoga studio.
- Secure bicycle storage.
- Library with open fireplace.
- Business centre with free WiFi.
- Board room facilities.
- Private dining room & open kitchen bar.
- Private lounge and cinema.
- Poker room.
- Tennis court & club facilities.
- Expansive roof garden with entertainment areas, BBQ and dining facilities.
Please contact Mo Mellak on 0405 083 188 or Katherine Liu on 0451 993 668 to find out more and to arrange a viewing.

Description:
Generous 1-Bedroom Apartment
Imagine coming home to enjoy the exciting lifestyle on offer in the NewQuay precinct with its restaurants, bars and shopping at your doorstep all with easy access from this sleek one bedroom apartment situated on the 14th floor of the distinctive landmark Nolan Tower. This apartment certainly has appeal for owner occupiers or an addition to a property portfolio. The interior features a spacious living & dining area opening to a full-width balcony providing scope for indoor/outdoor entertaining and Docklands precinct views; plus a sleek stainless steel kitchen with a bright red glass splash-back, a fully-tiled bathroom with separate bath and shower, laundry and car space.
Stylish & highly regarded
Great owner-occupier or investment potential
One bedroom, one bathroom + Euro laundry
High demand for these apartments
A sought-after NewQuay waterfront lifestyle
Spacious open-plan living with balcony & views
Walk-to all Docklands amenities & City
Intercom security entrance
Car space
Amenities
In keeping with this prestigious apartment complex additional amenities for residents include a fully equipped gymnasium, heated pool and rooftop outdoor entertaining area where you can enjoy the views and entertain your friends.
Location
There is so much to enjoy in the NewQuay precinct, with its easy access to the vibrant food and entertainment hub that is The District Docklands including the Hoyts Cinema, gourmet food shopping, the new Dan Murphys and The Melbourne Star Observation Wheel; plus an array of waterside restaurants and bars, Marvel Stadium for sports fans or the Capital City Bike Trail. Accessibility to the rest of Melbourne and some of the citys best universities is also taken care of thanks to nearby free trams, Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus service to Melbourne Airport when required.
Please contact Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293 or Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

Description:
A golden penthouse opportunity that is once in a lifetime!
Highlighted by remarkable 270 degree views and an utterly unique floorplan that promotes expansive formal and casual living, this opulent 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2 car space penthouse is an undisputed masterpiece. The Tower 1 complex is one of the most iconic in all of the Docklands, with this 31st floor apartment housed within the unique skewed gold glass box sitting on top of this Yarras Edge complex. This is genuine penthouse gold!
230 sqm (approx.) of total living space makes this one of the largest apartments in Yarras Edge
Incredible 270 degree views include the full city skyline, Yarra River and marina, mountain ranges to the east and west, Port Phillip Bay, Docklands Park, and Albert Park Lake
Enormous and free-flowing central zone offers formal lounge and dining with tranquil gas log fireplace
Protected entertainers balcony delivers CBD, river, lake, and bay views
Pristine kitchen overflows with style and promises stainless steel Miele/Smeg appliances plus integrated Fisher & Paykel fridge/freezer
Dedicated casual meals area right next to the kitchen
Wake up to city and bay views from the master bedroom which boasts dual mirrored built-in robes and double vanity ensuite with bidet
Other large bedrooms with BIRs feature sunset views over the bay
Stylish central bathroom wedged in between the two bedrooms
Additional powder room next to the laundry
Ducted heating and cooling
Secure intercom entry
2 secure basement car spaces
Storage cage
AMENITIES
Residents of the Tower 1 complex have access to RekDek which features a swimming pool, spa, steam room, sauna, and gym.
LOCATION
The Yarras Edge precinct is a popular choice for owner-occupiers looking for a quiet position that is also so close to all the delights of the CBD. Pick up a bargain at the nearby South Wharf DFO, while South Wharf Promenade really comes alive on Friday nights with an array of terrific bars and restaurants including Munich Brauhaus, The General Assembly, Bangpop, and Boho, just to name a few. Youre also not far from Crown Entertainment Complex, Victoria Harbour precinct, Etihad Stadium, Batman Park, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Smashing Price 1 Bedder on Docklands
This exquisite 1 bedder apartment in the cleverly designed Boutique residential complex in the Heart of the Docklands along Bourke Street. A north facing apartment provides plenty of natural light. Great open plan layout providing plenty of space for the dining and living area which adjoins a balcony overlooking a landscaped garden.
Modern galley kitchen with glass splashback, stone bench top and quality stainless steel appliances including Gas cooktop. Plenty of storage. Large dual access bedroom with built in mirrored robes. Stylish bathroom with twin access incorporates laundry nook.
Other features include
Reverse cycle split system air conditioner
Double glazed windows
Tiled flooring in kitchen and bathroom.
Security entrance
Location is just fantastic. Walking distance to Woolworth, Asian Supermarts, The Library at the Dock and the astounding cafes and eateries there for you to enjoy. Free tram zoned and just a short stroll to Southern Cross station.
Please contact Ary Tjin on 0423 891 891 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Quays Retreat with Stunning North Views
This open plan one bedroom apartment exudes stylish contemporary class and offers access to great facilities in the Quays residential complex.
This fantastic 10th floor apartment will have stunning appeal to both owner-occupiers and investors. Take advantage of relaxed living and meals zone, undercover balcony with exceptional views below, stone kitchen with glass splashback and stainless steel Miele appliances, bedroom with built-in robe and views, classy designer bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating/cooling, and secure intercom.
The Quays offers some of the best residential facilities in Melbourne including access to a Health Club featuring a pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and yoga studio, as well as a Resident's Club with library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room and cinema lounge. There is also a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
Love the surrounding NewQuay precinct attractions which include the popular The District Docklands, restaurants including Woolshed, Cargo, Wok on the Dock and Lotus Chinese Restaurant, Marvel Stadium, IGA X-Press supermarket and trams on Harbour Esplanade and Docklands Drive.
Current rental: $450 per week; lease expires 25/07/2020.

This building designed by DKO Architecture is an iconic building for NewQuay, Docklands and Melbourne. This superb apartment encompasses a stylishly contemporary interior and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light.

Description:
Style, space and spectacular views in a vibrant lifestyle locale
Flaunting breathtaking views from Victoria Harbour to Port Phillip Bay, this magnificent one-bedroom plus study apartment offers a flexible layout with spectacular indoor-outdoor appeal. Surrounded by Docklands many restaurants, cafés and bars, while just a free tram-ride into the CBD, the home provides an infinitely vivacious lifestyle, with literally everything at its door.
Perched on the twenty-sixth floor and spread with sleek Oak floors, the homes open plan layout and wide balcony delivers a light and airy feel, providing plenty of space to relax and dine with friends against a picture-perfect sunset view. The fully appointed kitchen makes catering a breeze, offering quality Miele cooking appliances and a handy dish-drawer among its stylish timber-look cabinetry.
A home office adds essential space for home-based work, while offering the flexibility as a separate dining room, while the generous robed bedroom entices a restful nights sleep against the glittery water-views, complemented by a stylish, fully tiled bathroom. Finished with a Euro laundry and secure carparking on title, and cocooned in todays best comfort and security, the home delivers a unique city-lifestyle, enriched by residents facilities including pool, spa, gym, library, business lounge and podium-level garden retreat.
Vacant possession now and private inspection could be organized at your convenience or during Christmas and New Year time.
Contact Nancy Jia 0430 770 820 for more details
